  "text": "Until now, most investigations about VOC of grassland focused on short-term cut-related emissions [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] Karl et al., 2001a, b, and [CITATION_3] . In this study we measured cutrelated as well as growth-related methanol emissions of two different grassland fields. We compare their integral contribution by referring them to the carbon content of the harvest yield (C Harvest ).",
